data.name: Mai Tai
data.quickTastyDescription: A refreshing tropical cocktail with a blend of rum, citrus, and almond flavors.
detailedCookingInstructions: In a shaker, combine the white rum, dark rum, orange curaçao, orgeat syrup, and lime juice.
Fill the shaker with ice and shake well until chilled.
Strain the mixture into a glass filled with crushed ice.
Garnish with mint leaves and a lime wedge.
